OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781614115
OL,3,CWorld Cup official says gesture
OL,4,Cresembling 'white power' sign caused
OL,5,Cby 'twitch'
OL,7,FA World Cup video assistant referee
OL,8,F(VAR) who faced backlash after making
OL,9,Fa hand gesture resembling a white
OL,10,Fsupremacist sign said it was caused by
OL,11,Fan "involuntary, subconscious twitch".
OL,13,FShaun Evans was cleared by Fifa after
OL,14,Fhe was found not to have breached
OL,15,Ffootball's disciplinary code.
OL,17,FThe Australian referee said he was
OL,18,F"unaware" he had made the sign and
OL,19,Fthat the incident and resulting
OL,20,Fcoverage "simply does not reflect who
OL,21,FI am".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
