FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781614115
OL,3,CWorld Cup official says gesture
OL,4,Cresembling 'white power' sign caused
OL,5,Cby 'twitch'
OL,7,FDespite being cleared, Fifa's
OL,8,Fdiscrimination monitor has called for
OL,9,FEvans to be removed from the
OL,10,Ftournament for the upside-down "OK"
OL,11,Fsymbol he made with his right hand
OL,12,Fafter officiating at Germany's opening
OL,13,F7-1 win over Curacao on Sunday.
OL,15,FIn a statement released by Fifa on
OL,16,FMonday, Evans said: "I did not
OL,17,Fintentionally make a hand gesture or
OL,18,Fsymbol to communicate a message,
OL,19,Faffiliation, game or belief of any
OL,20,Fkind."
OL,26,@uD@R{qxD@UOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781614115
OL,3,CWorld Cup official says gesture
OL,4,Cresembling 'white power' sign caused
OL,5,Cby 'twitch'
OL,7,F"The only explanation I can offer is
OL,8,Fthat the movement was an involuntary,
OL,9,Fsubconscious twitch, and I was unaware
OL,10,FI had done it at the time. Images
OL,11,Ftaken later during the match showed
OL,12,Fthat I repeated this movement many
OL,13,Ftimes while holding a pen between my
OL,14,Ffingers," he added.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
