FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781614115
OL,3,CWorld Cup official says gesture
OL,4,Cresembling 'white power' sign caused
OL,5,Cby 'twitch'
OL,7,FHe continued: "Of course, I understand
OL,8,Fhow the gesture has been interpreted
OL,9,Fand I regret this, however I want to
OL,10,Fbe very clear and categorically say
OL,11,Fthat I did not knowingly or
OL,12,Fdeliberately make the hand symbol
OL,13,Fsuggested. Officiating at the World
OL,14,FCup is the biggest honour of my career
OL,15,Fand I look forward to supporting my
OL,16,Fcolleagues for the rest of the
OL,17,Ftournament."
OL,26,@oD@OOUyD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
