OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781614115
OL,3,CWorld Cup official says gesture
OL,4,Cresembling 'white power' sign caused
OL,5,Cby 'twitch'
OL,7,FThe Fifa panel said in a statement:
OL,8,F"Fifa's independent disciplinary
OL,9,Fcommittee can confirm that, after
OL,10,Flooking into the matter involving
OL,11,Fsupport video assistant referee Shaun
OL,12,FEvans, it has found no evidence of
OL,13,Fbreaches of the Fifa disciplinary
OL,14,Fcode."
OL,16,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
