PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781614115
OL,3,CWorld Cup official says gesture
OL,4,Cresembling 'white power' sign caused
OL,5,Cby 'twitch'
OL,7,FThe gesture, with thumb and forefinger
OL,8,Ftouching in a circle and other fingers
OL,9,Foutstretched, was appropriated a
OL,10,Fdecade ago as a signal for white
OL,11,Fsupremacy that originated as a hoax on
OL,12,Fthe online message board 4chan before
OL,13,Fbeing adopted by some far-right groups.
OL,15,FThe sign attracted global attention in
OL,16,FMarch 2019 when it was made during the
OL,17,Ffirst court appearance of the white
OL,18,Fsupremacist who killed 51 Muslim
OL,19,Fworshippers at two mosques in
OL,20,FChristchurch.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
