FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781614115
OL,3,CWorld Cup official says gesture
OL,4,Cresembling 'white power' sign caused
OL,5,Cby 'twitch'
OL,7,FLater that year, it was designated a
OL,8,Fhate symbol by the New York-based Anti-
OL,9,FDefamation League.
OL,11,FFare network, a long-time partner of
OL,12,FFifa and Uefa that monitors racist and
OL,13,Fdiscriminatory chants, flags and
OL,14,Fsymbols at international games, said
OL,15,FEvans' gesture "clearly resembles an
OL,16,Fupside-down 'OK' hand symbol used as a
OL,17,F'white power' symbol in global far-
OL,18,Fright circles."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
