PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781614115
OL,3,CWorld Cup official says gesture
OL,4,Cresembling 'white power' sign caused
OL,5,Cby 'twitch'
OL,7,F"Clearly this official should have no
OL,8,Ffurther role to play in this World
OL,9,FCup," Fare said in its statement.
OL,11,FAustralia's Professional Football
OL,12,FReferees Association said it welcomed
OL,13,Fthe outcome of Fifa's review.
